# Blog Engine API (Express & Prisma)

A robust backend for a content management system (CMS) or blog, featuring relational data management between users and posts. This project demonstrates integration with PostgreSQL and the use of Prisma ORM for type-safe database operations.

## ğŸš€ Technologies

- **Node.js & Express**: Web framework and runtime.
- **Prisma ORM**: Modern database toolkit for PostgreSQL.
- **Supabase**: Cloud PostgreSQL database hosting.
- **Dotenv**: Environment variable management.

## ğŸ—ï¸ Database Schema

The API manages two main entities with a one-to-many relationship:
- **User**: Name and unique email.
- **Post**: Title, content, slug, and publication status, linked to an author.


